ğŸ› Troubleshooting
Common Issues
Authentication not working?

Verify Firebase configuration in config.js
Check that Authentication is enabled in Firebase Console
Ensure Google provider is configured if using Google sign-in

Tasks not saving?

Confirm Firestore rules allow user access
Check browser console for JavaScript errors
Verify internet connection for Firebase sync

Notifications not showing?

Allow notifications in browser settings
Check if notifications are blocked for the site
Verify task has due date and time set

